snippet.title: Hover : Revolt of Gamers - PC Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Experience the thrills of a fast-paced single and multiplayer Parkour game. Join the Rebellion and deride the security forces of an anti-leisure tyranny. Rise up to the many challenges of a futuristic Open World. Assemble your team, enhance your gear and perform incredible tricks and combos.

Steam : http://store.steampowered.com/app/280180/Hover__Revolt_Of_Gamers/

Official site : http://hover-rog.com/

Twitter : https://twitter.com/hover_the_game

Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/HoverRevoltOfGamers/

To discover our games, see : http://www.thesidek.com/
